### Behavr Collector — local defaults (no API key when profile is `local`)
### With profile `prod`: every POST needs `X-Behavr-Site-Key` (see @siteKey). Topic `behavr.events.raw` is auto-created at startup if your Confluent API key allows it; otherwise create the topic in the Confluent UI.
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@siteKey = test_secret_key

### Health (optional sanity check)
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Send batch — search (matches SDK / spec shape)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "site_id": "site_123",
  "sent_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:00Z",
  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "8f3dd1c7-0b7c-4baf-91a8-8f41d9d7d4c1",
      "event_type": "search",
      "site_id": "site_123",
      "anonymous_id": "anon_123",
      "session_id": "session_456",
      "occurred_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:00Z",
      "url": "https://shop.example.com/search?q=hoodie",
      "path": "/search",
      "title": "Search results",
      "referrer": "https://google.com",
      "user_agent": "Mozilla/5.0",
      "browser_language": "en-US",
      "device_type": "desktop",
      "sdk_version": "1.0.0",
      "utm": {
        "utm_source": "google",
        "utm_medium": "cpc"
      },
      "properties": {
        "query": "hoodie",
        "results_count": 12,
        "source": "live_input"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Send batch — page_view + product_view (two events)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "site_id": "site_123",
  "sent_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:01Z",
  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111",
      "event_type": "page_view",
      "site_id": "site_123",
      "anonymous_id": "anon_abc",
      "session_id": "sess_xyz",
      "occurred_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:01Z",
      "url": "https://shop.example.com/products",
      "path": "/products",
      "title": "Products",
      "referrer": null,
      "user_agent": "HTTP Client",
      "browser_language": "en-US",
      "device_type": "desktop",
      "sdk_version": "1.0.0",
      "utm": {},
      "properties": {
        "source": "http_file"
      }
    },
    {
      "event_id": "22222222-2222-4222-8222-222222222222",
      "event_type": "product_view",
      "site_id": "site_123",
      "anonymous_id": "anon_abc",
      "session_id": "sess_xyz",
      "occurred_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:02Z",
      "url": "https://shop.example.com/p/sku_123",
      "path": "/p/sku_123",
      "title": "Nike Hoodie",
      "referrer": "https://shop.example.com/products",
      "user_agent": "HTTP Client",
      "browser_language": "en-US",
      "device_type": "desktop",
      "sdk_version": "1.0.0",
      "utm": {},
      "properties": {
        "product_id": "sku_123",
        "product_name": "Nike Hoodie",
        "source": "http_file"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Same as first request but with site API key (use when not running `local` profile)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Behavr-Site-Key: {{siteKey}}

{
  "site_id": "site_123",
  "sent_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:00Z",
  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "aaaaaaaa-bbbb-4ccc-dddd-eeeeeeeeeeee",
      "event_type": "purchase",
      "site_id": "site_123",
      "anonymous_id": "anon_123",
      "session_id": "session_456",
      "occurred_at": "2026-05-15T12:00:00Z",
      "url": "https://shop.example.com/thanks",
      "path": "/thanks",
      "title": "Thank you",
      "referrer": "https://shop.example.com/checkout",
      "user_agent": "Mozilla/5.0",
      "browser_language": "en-US",
      "device_type": "desktop",
      "sdk_version": "1.0.0",
      "utm": {},
      "properties": {
        "order_id": "order_1001",
        "total": 159.98,
        "currency": "USD",
        "source": "http_file"
      }
    }
  ]
}
